author: Haley Lewis
text: Unlike a collector I don’t save my stamps I use them on cards and letters and I use the postal service quite often. I am afraid cards are going out of style :( and no one sends thank you notes anymore. Growing up my nana taught me thank you notes were a part of etiquette and that is just how it’s done… this world is going downhill — that’s another story for another time. These stamps are beautiful and will get people talking saying how elegant they are if you use them on letters or cards. I actually used these ones in particular on my best friend’s wedding thank you notes (which I did for her as a favor to help take some stress off of her after the big day — I was her maid of honor) anyways go ahead and see for yourself

author: Jose
text: Unlike a collector I don’t save my stamps I use them on cards and letters and I use the postal service quite often. I am afraid cards are going out of style :( and no one sends thank you notes anymore. Growing up my nana taught me thank you notes were a part of etiquette and that is just how it’s done… this world is going downhill — that’s another story for another time. These stamps are beautiful and will get people talking saying how elegant they are if you use them on letters or cards. I actually used these ones in particular on my best friend’s wedding thank you notes (which I did for her as a favor to help take some stress off of her after the big day — I was her maid of honor) anyways go ahead and see for yourself

author: Brena
text: Unlike a collector I don’t save my stamps I use them on cards and letters and I use the postal service quite often. I am afraid cards are going out of style :( and no one sends thank you notes anymore. Growing up my nana taught me thank you notes were a part of etiquette and that is just how it’s done… this world is going downhill — that’s another story for another time. These stamps are beautiful and will get people talking saying how elegant they are if you use them on letters or cards. I actually used these ones in particular on my best friend’s wedding thank you notes (which I did for her as a favor to help take some stress off of her after the big day — I was her maid of honor) anyways go ahead and see for yourself

These stamps are beautiful and will get people talking saying how elegant they are if you use them on letters or cards. author: Asie As
text: Unlike a collector I don’t save my stamps I use them on cards and letters and I use the postal service quite often. I am afraid cards are going out of style :( and no one sends thank you notes anymore.
